flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B[01 Scan / Snapshot]
  B --> C[02 Analysis / Classification / Recalibration / Output]
  C --> D[Build Handoff State]
  D --> E[02.5 Pre-Simulation Package]
  E --> F{Ready?}
  F -->|Isolation required| G[Isolation Add-On]
  G --> D
  F -->|Reattempt required| E
  F -->|Ready: all six conditions| H[03 Simulation Environment]
  H --> I{Simulation result}
  I -->|Transient| H
  I -->|Unresolved| G
  I -->|Passed| J[04 Replay / Proof]
  J --> K{Proof passed?}
  K -->|No| P[Preserve Result]
  K -->|Yes| L[05 User Apply / Cancel / Preserve]
  L -->|Cancel or preserve| P
  L -->|Apply| M[06 Explicit Apply Relay]
  M --> N[07 Post-Apply Verification]
  N --> O[08 Final Result Locked]
  P --> O
  O --> Z([End])
